 OHIO LONG RANGE PROGRAM FOR IMPROVEMENT OF LIBRARY SERVICES.     PRESENTS THE LONG TERM PROGRAMME FOR IMPROVING LIBRARY SERVICES IN OHIO USINGLIBRARY SERVICES AND CONSTRUCTION ACT (LSCA) FUNDS, ADOPTED BY THE STATELIBRARY BOARD IN SEPT 80. INCLUDES SEPARATE SECTIONS ON THE STATE LIBRARY,SERVICES TO THE DISABLED, PUBLIC, ACADEMIC, SCHOOL, SPECIAL, AND INSTITUTIONLIBRARIES, AND ADMINISTRATION AND CLASSES OF LSCA FUNDS